OL,6,FA former soldier who lost his leg
OL,7,Fwhile serving in the Army has
OL,8,Fdescribed his shock at finding out
OL,9,Fthat he was given as medics fought to
OL,10,Fsave his life.
OL,12,FBrendan West, who was born in , lost
OL,13,Fhis leg in 1979 and was given a blood
OL,14,Ftransfusion while at a British
OL,15,Fmilitary hospital in Germany.
OL,17,F40 years later, he discovered that the
OL,18,Fblood he was given was infected with
OL,19,FHepatitis C.
