OL,3,CEx-soldier who lost his leg in service
OL,4,Cand was given infected blood
OL,6,FMr West signed up to the Army in 1976
OL,7,Fand was deployed to a British Military
OL,8,Fbase in Germany as part of his work
OL,9,Fwith the Royal Electrical Mechanical
OL,10,FEngineers (REME).
OL,12,FWhile on duty outside of the barracks
OL,13,Fin 1979, Mr West was in a hit-and-run
OL,14,Fcar accident and suffered multiple
OL,15,Finjuries.
OL,17,FHe said his leg was "smashed to
OL,18,Fpieces", all of his ribs were broken
OL,19,Fand he also suffered a fractured elbow.
