OL,4,Cand was given infected blood
OL,6,FMr West said he was first treated at a
OL,7,FBelgian hospital and then was sent to
OL,8,Fa British military hospital in Germany.
OL,10,F"I still had my leg at the time, it
OL,11,Fwas smashed up," he said. "I was
OL,12,Fbecoming more and more ill ` I don't
OL,13,Fknow if it was gangrenous or not ` but
OL,14,Fthey had to amputate it and I was
OL,15,Fgiven a lot of blood.
