OL,6,FHe added: "I think the galling aspect
OL,7,Ffor me is that the way multiple
OL,8,Fgovernments, but particularly this
OL,9,FGovernment, have reacted (to the
OL,10,Finfected blood scandal)."
OL,12,F"Having served my country, and trying
OL,13,Fto have faith in the government, but
OL,14,Fall I see publicly is that they're
OL,15,Fkicking me while I'm down.
OL,17,F"I'm lucky to be alive ` there are so
OL,18,Fmany dead: children; mothers; fathers
OL,19,F` yet the government continue to delay
OL,20,Fby design."
