OL,6,FMr West was diagnosed after he tried
OL,7,Fto give blood during the coronavirus
OL,8,Fpandemic.
OL,10,F"During lockdown, I just wanted to do
OL,11,Fsomething good," he said.
OL,13,F"I went to give blood and I got a
OL,14,Fshock letter which came through the
OL,15,Fpost and said 'you have got Hepatitis
OL,16,FC antibodies, we can't take your
OL,17,Fblood'.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@PO]uD@AOU
