OL,3,CEx-soldier who lost his leg in service
OL,4,Cand was given infected blood
OL,6,FNow retired, he recalls various
OL,7,Fepisodes of unexplained illness during
OL,8,Fhis working life that he has now
OL,9,Frealised were caused by Hepatitis C.
OL,11,F"I had numerous unexplained illnesses
OL,12,Fand episodes of exhaustion, which
OL,13,Faffected my working life in a big
OL,14,Fway," he said.
OL,16,F"I worked hard and progressed while
OL,17,Fsuffering bouts of illness and periods
OL,18,Fof exhaustion.
