OL,6,F"At one point I was offered a
OL,7,Fpromotion which would involve lots of
OL,8,Finternational travel but I had to turn
OL,9,Fit down because I knew I wasn't
OL,10,Fphysically able to take on that role."
OL,12,FMr West, who was born in Colne,
OL,13,FLancashire, needs aids to get around
OL,14,Fincluding prosthetics, crutches,
OL,15,Fwalking sticks and a wheelchair.
OL,17,FHe continued: "After the diagnosis, it
OL,18,Fwas discovered that I have pretty
OL,19,Fsevere liver damage as well so I'm
OL,20,Fmonitored every six months for liver
OL,21,Fcancer, which is a likely end for me.
