OL,6,F"I also have varices in the
OL,7,Foesophagus... I've tried to be
OL,8,Fpositive about things... but I've been
OL,9,Ftold I might bleed to death when they
OL,10,Fburst.
OL,12,F"Psychologically it has affected me
OL,13,Freally badly."
OL,15,FHe added: "It has dramatically
OL,16,Faffected me and the worst part about
OL,17,Fit is seemingly the Government is
OL,18,Ftotally uncaring about it."
