OL,6,FMr West ` who now lives in Hampshire,
OL,7,Fwith his cat Shorty ` said that he
OL,8,F"kept pretty quiet" about his
OL,9,Fdiagnosis.
OL,11,F"It has taken a lot for me to speak to
OL,12,Fpeople about it, but now things are
OL,13,Fcoming to a head because of the lack
OL,14,Fof government activity, I have decided
OL,15,Fto speak up."
OL,17,FHe decided to share his story ahead of
OL,18,Fthe final report of in the Infected
OL,19,FBlood Inquiry, which is due to be
OL,20,Fpublished on May 20.
