OL,6,FRachel Halford, chief executive of The
OL,7,FHepatitis C Trust, said: "For decades,
OL,8,Fpeople who received infected blood or
OL,9,Fblood products, and their loved ones,
OL,10,Fwere stigmatised, vilified and
OL,11,Fdisbelieved."
OL,13,F"Brendan's story highlights the many
OL,14,Fways in which people impacted by the
OL,15,Finfected blood scandal have been and
OL,16,Fcontinue to be let down at every
OL,17,Fpossible stage by consecutive
OL,18,Fgovernments."
